.SS Event delegation
There are two ways of implementing event delegation for this event: by
using the \f[CR]focusout\f[R] event, or by setting the
\f[CR]useCapture\f[R] parameter of \f[CR]addEventListener()\f[R] to
\f[CR]true\f[R].
.SS HTML
